para_trans: Mauje Khandali, Ta. Regarding sanction of Primary Health Centre at Ahmedpur, G. Latur.
Government Decision No: Proceeds-2024 / No.108 / Health-4

Read: - Letter No. of Joint Director, Health Services, (Pre-Centre / Sub-Centre / Clinics), Mumbai: Go to No. 7A / Room-7A / T-8 / Khandali / Pre-Centre / Establishment / Latur / 1122-24/2024, dated 27.02.2024.
Preface: - Mouje Khandali, Ta. Health facilities to the citizens of the area at Ahmedpur, District Latur
A new primary health centre needs to be sanctioned in line with the provision of primary health care at the site.
The issue of sanctioning a health centre was under the consideration of the government. The following decisions are being taken in this regard:
Government Decision: - Mouje Khandali, Ta. New Primary Health Centre sanctioned as "Special Case" at Ahmedpur, District Latur
2. Acquisition of space for this Primary Health Centre in the prescribed manner at the site of the Primary Health Centre.
Separate action on construction of health centre, post creation from district planning fund
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
